text: "Lego House" is a 2011 song by English singer-songwriter Ed Sheeran and is the third single from his debut studio album +. It went to the top 20 in Australia, Belgium, Ireland, Israel, Lebanon, New Zealand and the United Kingdom. It also peaked at number 42 in the United States and number 54 in Canada.
